data.description: Less than 1/2 mile from North Smithfield high school, and middle school… cozy 2-3 bedroom vinyl sided ranch. Spacious master bedroom with double closets. A small second bedroom off living room, a full bathroom with tub and shower and   Lots of country charm flows into the living room and dining room to the kitchen area with a convenient laundry area including washer and new dryer hidden away on the first level. There is also  an oversized attached garage off of the kitchen . The house has replacement windows throughout.  Attic storage, In 2021 RISE did blown in insulation in the ceilings and walls for super efficiency- there is a full basement that is totally Dry with a DRY ZONE basement  system Installed 2019 with two sump pumps.  Also has a radon reduction system in place and has an easy generator full house hook up with 200 amp circuit breaker, electrical. Newer septic system was installed 2016.  The Roof , plumbing , electrical  and heat systems all within the last 8 years too. Plenty of basement storage space.  The finished side of basement has a very large space with closet that can be used as a 3rd bedroom or a family room or office . Outside there is an empty   Chicken coop and nice outdoor space of almost a half acre (0.44acres) Easy access to 295, 146, .parking for 5 cars easily …. come and see this north Smithfield charmer …
